content.title: Status of Aurea Monitor Fix Deployment
content.visibleText:
Status of Aurea Monitor Fix Deployment

Hi Team,

Please find attached the presentation slides I initially had at the inception of the project (with PDF slides for the existing issues).

As some of you are aware, we have been in a position to fix most of the major issues with our monitoring system. However, there are still a few issues that need to be addressed in the next patch, which will require some more time.

Our current implementation allows us to:

- Monitor and control the system remotely.

- Automatically detect and report errors.

- Provide a comprehensive overview of the system's performance.

Please let me know if you have any questions or would like to provide feedback on the slides or any of the key talking points we should address.

Thank you,

George
